          p.text-main.case__text From pre-seed to series, we accelerate the companies we believe in by generating serious brand equity, product traction, and market-penetrating strategies.

  section.section-work
    .container
      .container__inside
        h3.title-h2.section__title We were working with.
        p.text-main.section__text From pre-seed to series, we accelerate the companies we believe in by generating serious brand equity, product traction, and market-penetrating strategies.

        .section-work__works
          - for (var x = 1; x < 10; x++)
            img(src=`/img/work/item-${x}.svg`, alt="")

  section.section-internal
    .container
      .container__inside
        h3.title-h3.section__title Our internal projects.
        p.text-main.section__text From pre-seed to series, we accelerate the companies we believe in by generating serious brand equity, product traction.
