          p.text-main.case__text From pre-seed to series, we accelerate the companies we believe in by generating serious brand equity, product traction, and market-penetrating strategies.
        
        a(href="#").link-main.section__more More our projects

  section.section-about
    .container
      .container__inside
        h2.title-h2.section__title There is something to read about.
